          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2278Step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the quinoa is cooked, remove from the heat and leave to steam-dry, uncovered, until serving</p><p>Meanwhile, pat your <strong>rump steak[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the steak[s] to a plate with your <strong>ground cumin</strong>, 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and turn until coated</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thick strips</p>",
