            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the steak is cooking, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>into quarters</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> to a bowl with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
