      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>coriander & parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong> and cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped parsley</strong>, <strong>coriander</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a small splash of <strong>cold water</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
