            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grind the herbs to a paste, then add your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> – this is your <strong>chimichurri yoghurt</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the <strong>stone</strong></p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and slice finely lengthways</p>",
      "order": 7,
